            "body": "I've found what causes this issue:\r\n`let g:rustfmt_autosave = 1`\r\n\r\nafter figuring this out, I found out that there is a github issue for that: https://github.com/rust-lang/rust.vim/issues/381\r\n\r\n\r\nclosing this issue, since I could resolve it by setting above directive to `0`.",
